snippet.title: Inside the Arena: Introducing PlanetSide Arena
snippet.description:
Executive Producer Andy Sites and Lead Designer Tony Morton share development insights and debut the trailer for PlanetSide Arena, launching January 29, 2019.
Learn more and pre-order now: https://www.planetsidearena.com

Follow PlanetSide Arena on:
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/planetsidearena
Twitter - https://www.twitter.com/planetsidearena
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/planetsidearena
Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/planetsidearena
